text: This coffee shop is inside a cluster of HDB flats at the corner of Jalan Bukit Merah and Lower Delta Road. It has just 5 stalls - drinks stall, fishball noodles stall, porridge stall, roast meat stall and a Muslim food stall. The most popular stalls are the fishball noodles and porridge stall. These two stalls are definitely worth the trip to go n

The drink stall teh and kopi were quite good. The prawn crackers and youtiao were delicious too.

There were stalls selling fishball noodles, Cantonese roast meats, porridge and malay food but all were closed when I was there at 2pm.
Very nice Mee pork authentic flavor at coffeeshop. A must try..
Iced coffee in a cup is now at $1.70
Very good meepok with alot chillies
